title: Soup Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Beer/Wine, Caribbean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A canteen, bar and live music venue offers vegan menu choices, including a vegan roast on Sundays. Located in the northern quarter. Free Wi-Fi. Encompasses two floors and in addition to live music, also hosts club nights, film nights, comedy events and art exhibitions.
